# EW Spectrum View — D3.js Rules

## Chart Configuration
- **X-axis**: Log scale, 400 MHz – 6,000 MHz (6 GHz)
- **Y-axis**: Signal strength / threat level (0–100 normalised)
- **Width**: Full container width, responsive
- **Height**: Minimum 300px

## Frequency Gridlines (always rendered)
| Frequency | Label | Why |
|---|---|---|
| 433 MHz | 433 | Common ISM / FPV band |
| 900 MHz | 900 | Long-range RC (ExpressLRS, ELRS) |
| 1,227 MHz | L2 | GPS L2 |
| 1,575 MHz | L1 | GPS L1 (primary civilian) |
| 2,400 MHz | 2.4G | DJI C2, WiFi |
| 5,800 MHz | 5.8G | FPV video, DJI Occusync |

## Band Colour Coding (fixed — do not change)
```ts
const BAND_COLORS = {
  gnss:   '#06B6D4',  // cyan   — GPS, GLONASS, Galileo, BeiDou
  c2:     '#F97316',  // orange — command & control / datalink
  video:  '#EF4444',  // red    — FPV video feeds
  radar:  '#10B981',  // green  — radar emissions
  comms:  '#A855F7',  // purple — comms / SATCOM
  jammer: '#F59E0B',  // amber  — jammer overlay bands
}
```

